# hellocashAPI v1

## Authentication

To authenticate your requests with the helloCash API, you have to use your bearer token.

###### Bearer Token Authentication
- register for a helloCash account at https://myhellocash.com/start-now-blue
- navigate to > Cash Register > Settings > General > helloCash API
- generate a token
- include the token in the authorization header of your API requests
- Note: API is only available in DEMO, PREMIUM and GASTRO mode.
- Example Header:
    + Request

        + Headers

                Authorization: Bearer YOURTOKEN

## Character encoding

Only unescaped unicode should be sent to the API, otherwise it may be that our firewall is blocking the request (403).
The API itself returns the data in escaped form (e.g. ü => \u00fc)

