## Invoices [/invoices]

### Get a list of invoices [GET /invoices{?limit,offset,search,dateFrom,dateTo,mode,showDetails}]
+ Request (application/json)

    + Headers

            Authorization: Bearer <token>

+ Parameters
    + limit (integer, optional) - maximum number of returned invoices (max 1000)
        + Default: 1000
    + offset (integer, optional) - `offset/page (a offset of 2 with limit 1000 gives the invoices 1001 - 2000)`
        + Default: 1
    + search (string, optional) - search for an invoice with a specific number or customer
    + dateFrom (string, optional) - set from-date ('dateTo'-Parameter has to be set!)
    + dateTo (string, optional) - set to-date ('dateFrom'-Parameter has to be set!)
    + mode (string, optional) - set mode=test to get test invoices
    + showDetails (boolean, optional) - get more invoice details, e.g. positions or customer

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Attributes
        + invoices (array[SimpleInvoice], required, fixed-type) - array of returned invoices
        + Include PaginationMixin

### Get a specific invoice [GET /invoices/{id}]
+ Parameters
    + id: 1 (integer, required) - system ID of the invoice

+ Request (application/json)

    + Headers

            Authorization: Bearer <token>

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (CanceledInvoice, required, fixed-type)
        + paymentMethods (array[PaymentMethodInvoice], optional) - list of payment methods when `invoice_payment` is "Kombiniert"

### Get a specific invoice as PDF [GET /invoices/{id}/pdf{?cancellation,locale}]
+ Parameters
    + id: 1 (integer, required) - system ID of the invoice
    + cancellation (boolean, optional) - get the invoice cancellation instead if true
        + Default: false
    + locale: es_ES (enum[string], optional) - set language for pdf
        + Members
            + `de_AT`
            + `de_DE`
            + `en_GB`
            + `es_ES`
            + `fr_FR`
            + `cs_CZ`
            + `pl_PL`
        + Default: `en_GB`

+ Request (application/json)

    + Headers

            Authorization: Bearer <token>

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Attributes
        + pdf_base64_encoded: JVBERi0xLjQKMyAwIG9iago8PC9UeXBlIC9QYWdlCi9QYXJlbgPDw... (string, required) - base64 encoded pdf

### Create a new invoice [POST /invoices]
+ Request (application/json)

    + Headers

            Authorization: Bearer <token>

    + Attributes
        + cashier_id: 679 (number) - cashier system id
            + Default: 0
        + invoice_testMode (boolean) - true if a test invoice should be created
            + Default: false
        + invoice_text: `Thanks for buying!` (string) - additional text on the invoice
        + invoice_reference (boolean) - does the invoice reference an existing one
            + Default: false
        + invoice_paymentMethod: cash (string) - payment method used for the invoice
            + Default: Bar
        + invoice_discount_percent: 5 (number) - number of percent given as discount on the invoice
            + Default: 0
        + invoice_type: json (enum[string]) - output format for the invoice response
            + Members
                + `json`
                + `pdf`
                + `receipt`
                + `digital`
        + locale: es_ES (enum[string]) - set language for pdf / receipt
            + Members
                + `de_AT`
                + `de_DE`
                + `en_GB`
                + `es_ES`
                + `fr_FR`
                + `cs_CZ`
                + `pl_PL`
            + Default: `en_GB`
        + invoice_user_id: 6553 (number) - optional id of existing customer
        + signature_mandatory: true (boolean) - Invoice signing must be enabled and possible or invoice creation fails
        + items (array[CreateItem], required) - array of invoice positions


+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Description: `invoice_type: json` or not set
    + Attributes (ExtendedInvoice, required, fixed-type)
        + invoice_cancellation: 0 (string, required) - was the invoice canceled or not

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Description: `invoice_type: pdf`
    + Attributes (object)
        + pdf_base64_encoded: `JVBERi0xLjQK...` (string) - The PDF encoded as a base64 string
        + invoice_id: 6037 (number) - The ID of the created invoice

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Description: `invoice_type: receipt`
    + Attributes (object)
        + html: `<!DOCTYPE html><html lang="de">...` (string) - Full encoded HTML content to render/print the receipt
        + invoice_id: 6037 (number) - The ID of the created invoice

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Description: `invoice_type: digital`
    + Attributes (object)
        + link: `https://myhellocash.com/invoice/95822?token=...&preview=1` (string) - Public invoice preview link
        + text: `Your invoice from Musterfirma\n` (string) - Email or display text
